 impairment, diabetes, old age, severe or worsening heart failure, dehydration, or concomitant therapy with other agents that increase serum potassium such as nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs, beta-blockers, cyclosporine, heparin, tacrolimus, and trimethoprim.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/108305/', '', 'Amlodipine, Sacubitril, Hydrochlorothiazide, Nebivolol', '', 1767369485);
